Type: Package
Package: ellipsoidgaussian
Title: Fit an Ellipsoid-Gaussian Distribution
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Hanyu Song
Maintainer: Hanyu Song <songhanyu1211@gmail.com>
Description: An ellipsoid-Gaussian multivariate distribution is induced
    when we use a Gaussian linear factor model, with the latent variables
    having a von Mises-Fisher distribution on a unit hyper-sphere and integrate
    over the latent variables w.r.t. its distributions.
    
    This package fits an ellipsoidn Gaussian latent factor model, which is used to model curved data (such as data on an ellipsoid). The ellipsoid-Gaussian distribution is induced when we use a Gaussian linear factor model with latent variables following a â€¦
